    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7307045>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Carteronius sudanus (Karsch, 1880) comb. nov.: A male, dorsal view; B same, lateral view; C same, ventral view; D female, dorsal view; E same, lateral view; F same, ventral view. Scale: 2 mm." ;
